name: Dust.TMOV83
description:
Welcome to The TMOV Visual art project.
TMOV Means: The mental world of a Visual artist from the Middle East.
Each piece Of this collection has a unique idea that contains a message or a feeling for the people of the world.
TMOV Project seeks to create a new visual language for communication between people of all races of the world. 
So become a member of the big TMOV family by buying nfts from this collection.
Limited Versions!

Artist: @erfanahmadi32
